reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 16, 2023
reviews.reviewText: As advertised and delivered on time and good quality computer mice. There's still a clicking sound but it's softened and it is so satisfying to click. Doesn't drive me nuts with the regular mice without the dampening.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 17, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Wow is all I can say, the quality and near silent clicks (literally), of this mouse are amazing
reviews.reviewText: -Incredible price for what you get, I've tested a lot of quiet mouses through the years, and this is close to completely silent, it actually has gotten more quiet over the short time I've used it. On a scale of 1 to 100, 100 being pure silence, I would say it's realistically right around 95-98.-The roller wheel is silent when turning it, and when the wheel is pressed in while you're rolling it. But it's not silent when pressing it.-The DPI button is not silent when clicking to change the cursor speed, but who cares? I don't use it much.-Extremely impressed, I just bought 4 more. Comfortable in the hand too! Haven't spilled anything on it yet, will be curious to see what happens when that does happen.-12/19/20, add to review: still super quiet and no issues thus far
